➜喜迎中秋，郑州一炒鸡店宴请60名环卫工吃团圆饭
http://www.sohu.com/a/420717787_528362	2822
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=216224259&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p>2020年9月23日上午11点50分许，郑州宏明路与柳西路交叉口西100米路南，一家名为老庄户炒鸡店门口呈现一片橙色海洋，60名来自国基路办事处的环卫工人端坐在小方桌前，津津有味吃着香喷喷的炒鸡，畅所欲言，每个人脸上都洋溢着灿烂的笑容。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200925/bbec1689610d4310a56256a010031df2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/31342fdbd1304b1b8965e767c84a96fa.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200925/56224cc19c594932b99d5ebc17e194a1.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
